
### Read all users
GET http://localhost:1218/user-api/users

### Read a user by id
GET http://localhost:1218/user-api/users/1


### Create new user
POST http://localhost:1218/user-api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "id":1,
    "name":"Madhurima",
    "age":19
}

### Update the existing user
PUT http://localhost:1218/user-api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "id":1,
    "name":"Akash",
    "age":13
}

### Delete the existing user by Id
DELETE http://localhost:1218/user-api/users/1

